{"tid":1216303,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我建議大家去金鐘嘅時候記得帶生果去食","createTime":"2019-06-13T09:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T16:00:58.000Z","uid":207665,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"58bc94e5c26cdb3898d9bdbf21ebc808b1a7f57d","tid":1216303,"uid":207665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:46:39.000Z","msg":"昨日小弟都身處現場<br />\n我見到好多人其實都食唔落野<br />\n但點都唔可以唔食<br />\n所以我覺得呢d高熱量既生果好啱大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完d皮仲好有用<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0iBznQM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0iBznQM.png&h=d2d9bd16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a29efab3114e53aec81d7f4f15b33d83c2d0bad","tid":1216303,"uid":207665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"推比大家知"},{"pid":"f5462b7598648f33c5fa8224100b783d3d69d8d4","tid":1216303,"uid":207665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddd4b559bd0499397eae419da7e8a43ddef02be7","tid":1216303,"uid":207665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1844e92597f487e337dd1da86783b13a358d7c25","tid":1216303,"uid":207665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d3ff14ea1342e07bc5309894dd05cc903e4b3e0","tid":1216303,"uid":202912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"pushh<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac89eef83110b92a13b29e8d06a29162f1b1034b","tid":1216303,"uid":74954,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:06:40.000Z","msg":"呢樣無意思 <br />\n看來危險  但又對full gear警察無傷害力<br />\n<br />\n一定要用軟食物  蕃茄 雞蛋 有用好多<br />\n去模糊佢頭盔視野 同